snippet.title: Best VGM 726 - The Violinist of Hameln - Inside the Crimson Castle
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
The Violinist of Hameln / Hamelin no Violin Tamaki (1995)
Inside the Crimson Castle
Y. Mori
